00:00:35.330 --> 00:00:37.010
It's November 7.

00:00:37.010 --> 00:00:39.980
What just happened?

00:00:39.980 --> 00:00:42.980
Part of the answer
is I don't totally

00:00:42.980 --> 00:00:45.230
know yet what my
